  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the trial is to demonstrate the effect of B. lactis in reducing the incidence
      of Necrotizing Enterocolitis (NEC) compared to placebo in preterm infants.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
